{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b3fe84b70d","title":"江青戚本禹在北京轻工业学院会见学生代表时的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1c25ef6e82","index":0,"year":1966,"month":7,"day":26,"articleId":"b3fe84b70d","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"对话","id":"314ad57c4d","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"戚本禹","id":"57434e107b","type":"人物"},{"name":"江青","id":"82305e518c","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"421124ccd3","name":"江青"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9dae1fc00b","type":"title","text":"江青戚本禹在北京轻工业学院会见学生代表时的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b3fe84b70d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f65e05e023","type":"paragraph","text":"〖江青戚本禹在北京轻工业学院会见了反工作组的学生的代表〗","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b3fe84b70d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"608885e7bf","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b3fe84b70d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7d8572606a","type":"paragraph","text":"这里都是自己人，谁也不会传出去。你们来的信，我们都看了，你们这样做，是热爱党中央和毛主席！我们有你们这样的接班人，中国不会变颜色。向你们说两点：","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b3fe84b70d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"82dee0c39f","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）你们是受迫害的，他们那样做，只有反革命才干得出来。要是再对你们进行迫害，就是现行反革命。他们对你们是怎么迫害的？你们回去准备材料，准备控诉。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b3fe84b70d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4a4dbf63ad","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）不应该死，应挺起腰杆革命，你们要是死了，问题就搞不清楚了。与其自杀，不如干革命，让敌人给一刀，这样还光荣。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b3fe84b70d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1ecfdc5f18","type":"paragraph","text":"你们学校是要夺权的！工作队、党委可以不信任嘛，反对工作队、常委，不一定是反对党中央和毛主席。党中央和毛主席根本没派过这样的工作队，一个也没派过。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b3fe84b70d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"41a3f0221b","type":"paragraph","text":"这样的工作队光撤了还不行，还要斗它。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b3fe84b70d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5748133d48","type":"paragraph","text":"你们来时，他们知道不知道？要是知道了，他们又要布置了，又想溜了。你们回去后要串联，要准备材料，简单扼要，要击中要害。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b3fe84b70d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"80e8ecfece","type":"paragraph","text":"你们敢不敢控诉？（答：敢！）我们给你们撑腰！我们要排着队去。你们讲话后，我们还要讲话。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b3fe84b70d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"372c63f67e","type":"paragraph","text":"你们要注意斗争策略，你们之间的分歧是工作队挑起的。不要把群众放在后边，不要光靠你们几个人。不要互相斗争，要争取中间群众。工作队员也会起义。同学说了一两句话错话，做了一两件错事，没关系。那些大人物说了些错话不算，为什么要对同学抓小辫子呢！","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b3fe84b70d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8e47ce78f3","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b3fe84b70d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"eb2620decb","type":"paragraph","text":"前一个工作队包庇黑帮，被他们赶走了。后一个还是这样。他们说开门整顿十天，实际想蒙混过关。邓是个不小的官儿呢，可这个人糊里糊涂，连话也说不清楚。上次做了报告，想把责任推到同学身上。上次我在那儿看大字报，点名的全是学生，有几十个，实际上都是他们指挥的。","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b3fe84b70d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4890cfa911","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b3fe84b70d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0d00b5fcd1","type":"paragraph","text":"你们回去，把精确数字统计上来。他们不是要找“后台”吗？我做你们的“后台”。毛主席给你们撑腰！","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b3fe84b70d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e0eb15b4d2","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b3fe84b70d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0ad857f5a2","type":"paragraph","text":"你们学校还有“党委领导万万岁”大字报，连这样的党委也保卫？！连反对毛泽东思想的院党委也要保卫？！","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b3fe84b70d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3385684126","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b3fe84b70d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6d0488e1bc","type":"paragraph","text":"你们回去要好好干，你们是主人嘛！","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b3fe84b70d","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}